;
;   GETPROPERTY ***********************************************************************
;
;    Purpose:
;
;       Allows the user to obtain the current properties of the object.
;
;    Definition:
;
;       PRO DrawColors::GetProperty, NAMES=names, RED=red, GREEN=green, BLUE=blue, $
;           STARTINDEX=startindex, NCOLORS=ncolors
